{"title":"Eddy Merckx Launches Three New Corsa Steel Models","link":"https://theradavist.com/eddy-merckx-launches-three-new-corsa-steel-models/","date":1715782094000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1411\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?fit=1200,1411&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?resize=1200,784&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?resize=2000,1306&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?resize=768,502&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?resize=1536,1003&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-0076_web.jpg?resize=2048,1338&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>After the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/eddy-merckx-steel-bikes-2024/\" target=\"_blank\">relaunch earlier this year</a>, <a href=\"https://www.eddymerckx.com/en_US\" target=\"_blank\">Eddy Merckx</a> now introduces the revamped Corsa range: high-quality bicycles featuring Columbus steel. Corsa is now available in three versions: a road bike, an all-road bike, and a gravel bike. Let’s check them out below.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5796-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The road bike is named ‘Corsa Mendrisio’: a fast all-round road bike.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5791-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The all-road bike is called ‘Corsa Pévèle’: depending on the tire choice, you can use the bike on the road or on gravel.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-5783-DMNRS_web.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Finally, there’s our favorite, the ‘Corsa Strasbourg’: a purebred gravel bike.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/EM-Corsa-Product-Strasbourg-0041_web.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Each of these three models is available in five sizes, from xs to xl. Their geometry is comparable to that of their carbon counterparts. The Corsa bikes are equipped with a Universal Derailleur Hanger (UDH). Harkoning back to the 1980s, the Corsa line is made with Columbus tubes, the reference in the world of steel bikes. A mix of Columbus Zona and Columbus SL tubes is used.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.eddymerckx.com/en_US\" target=\"_blank\">Eddy Merckx</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/eddy-merckx-launches-three-new-corsa-steel-models/\">Eddy Merckx Launches Three New Corsa Steel Models</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"877ca68a412d8c588010eea9a8db504a9c10340950a0d9e2c6bdbb0bb0db206d","category":"Cycling"}